&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration: &lt;/strong&gt;The Apprenticeship will typically take 18 – 24 months to complete, although the exact duration will be dependent on the previous experience of the individual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Review: &lt;/strong&gt;This Apprenticeship standard will be reviewed after 3 years.&lt;/p&gt;
